    "description": "加群审批测试资格：①：497400812 ②：849695089 ③：397112105<br>本游戏部分美术素材已购买获得封灵档案GKD工作室授权。<br><br>UE4报错及常见问题解决办法：<br>1.游戏无法登录提示链接失败或者未链接steam，则使用加速器加速一下社区，登录steam好友系统。   2.若游戏启动时打开UE4报错则可以重装或更新steam，或者是重装或者更新epic平台（有关联功能）。 3.缺少游戏运行环境，请根据提示安装C++或者相应提示的运行环境。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你有一夜暴富的梦想吗？那就来《赏金游戏》中实现这个梦想吧！！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/02af0338b3d17895c08b8db7af3d80df.poster.avif?t=1673136577\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/02af0338b3d17895c08b8db7af3d80df.webm?t=1673136577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/02af0338b3d17895c08b8db7af3d80df.mp4?t=1673136577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>各位参赛者，欢迎来到《赏金游戏》，一个人性的至暗舞台！你将与来自世界各地的挑战者们赌上性命，闯过五个随机的死亡关卡，争夺唯一的巨额奖金。<br>胜者只有一个，除了预判层出不穷的致命陷阱，你还需要提防来自其他参赛者的明枪暗箭。在这场致命的财富争夺战中，你会是主角，还是他人的垫脚石呢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/ba377ddef9e2c01bc3e059220671f6c3.avif?t=1673136577\" width=616 height=144 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/6b34fedb4a1a699389b198a283ff1dbc.poster.avif?t=1673136577\" width=626 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/6b34fedb4a1a699389b198a283ff1dbc.webm?t=1673136577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最高50人的同台竞技，但最后的赢家只有一个！</h2>来自世界各地的50位参赛者同台竞技，经典的儿时游戏暗藏危机。你的目标只有一个，排除所有阻碍获得唯一的最终大奖。<br>可以在游戏内像鱿鱼游戏一样，结成团体，或者叫上好友抱团在残酷的大逃杀中生存下来<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/deb575e49059b07d4647aa40bdd66ad6.avif?t=1673136577\" width=616 height=144 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/cc40182bf14aff8e2d2516ae2ab30201.poster.avif?t=1673136577\" width=616 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/cc40182bf14aff8e2d2516ae2ab30201.webm?t=1673136577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机的关卡模式，让每局比赛都有新鲜感</h2>进入比赛后，你将面对的是随机关卡连续挑战，每轮将从数个固定关卡之中随机抽取。胜利不可复制，失败不会再现，每次开局都是新的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/8f2807b3d44a578a2f045de7ecb44909.avif?t=1673136577\" width=616 height=144 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/704275ef92a5bc6ee20ac10709a256ee.poster.avif?t=1673136577\" width=626 height=213 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/704275ef92a5bc6ee20ac10709a256ee.webm?t=1673136577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >惊险刺激的互动PK，永远不要相信周围的人</h2>在比赛中，每一位玩家在进入关卡前可以选择一个专属的装备：棒球，叉子，拳套。拿起你的装备，有效地淘汰掉与你作对的竞争对手吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1805360/extras/278d28fc07e38afa451ca313309c9ccb.avif?t=1673136577\" width=616 height=144 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >夺得丰厚的奖金，登上游戏的顶峰</h2>使用奖金开启宝箱，你将能入手酷炫性感各式时装。再入赛场，你就是全场最靓的赏金之王。",
